SQL.SQLRaw: SELECT c.Codigo_Cuenta,c.Desc_Cuenta,c.Cod1,c.Cod3,c.Cod5,c.Cod7, CASE WHEN c.Cod1='1' THEN 'ACTIVO' ELSE 'PASCAP' END AS APC, (SELECT concat(a.hola1,'*', a.hola2) FROM (SELECT min(Fecha_Desde) as hola1, max(Fecha_Hasta) as hola2 FROM mt01peco WHERE Periodo BETWEEN '00' AND '09') as a) as fechas, (SELECT Desc_Cuenta FROM en01cuen WHERE Codigo_Cuenta=c.Cod1) AS Desc1, (SELECT Desc_Cuenta FROM en01cuen WHERE Codigo_Cuenta=c.Cod3) AS Desc3, (SELECT Desc_Cuenta FROM en01cuen WHERE Codigo_Cuenta=c.Cod5) AS Desc5, (SELECT Desc_Cuenta FROM en01cuen WHERE Codigo_Cuenta=c.Cod7) AS Desc7, (SELECT EsdeMovimiento FROM en01cuen WHERE Codigo_Cuenta=c.Cod7) AS esdemov7, [ {nivelCuenta}] as nivel, c.TotCred as TotCred, c.TotDeb as TotDeb, c.SaldoAnt AS SaldoAnt, C.TotDeb-C.TotCred as SaldoPer,C.TotDeb-C.TotCred+CASE WHEN c.SaldoAnt is null THEN 0 ELSE c.SaldoAnt END as SaldoActual FROM (SELECT a.Codigo_Cuenta,a.Desc_Cuenta, LEFT(a.Codigo_Cuenta,1) AS Cod1,LEFT(a.Codigo_Cuenta,3) AS Cod3,LEFT(a.Codigo_Cuenta,5) AS Cod5,LEFT(a.Codigo_Cuenta,7) AS Cod7, CASE WHEN {acumper} <> 'NULL' THEN (SELECT SUM(Total_Debitos - Total_Creditos)*1 FROM dt01cuen WHERE Codigo_Cuenta=a.Codigo_Cuenta [and Periodo between CASE WHEN Codigo_Cuenta like '1%' OR Codigo_Cuenta like '2%' OR Codigo_Cuenta like '3%' THEN '00' ELSE CASE WHEN {acumpercn} <> 'NULL' THEN {acumpercn} ELSE NULL END END and CASE WHEN {desdeper} <'01' THEN '..' ELSE RIGHT(CONCAT('00',(CAST({desdeper} AS INT)-1)),2) END]) ELSE 0 END as SaldoAnt, sum(b.Total_Debitos) as TotDeb,sum(b.Total_Creditos) as TotCred FROM dt01cuen b join en01cuen a on b.Codigo_Cuenta=a.Codigo_Cuenta WHERE (1=1) [AND len(a.Codigo_Cuenta) <= {nivelCuenta}] [AND (b.Periodo between {desdeper} and {hastaper})] [AND ((Len(b.Codigo_Cuenta) = {nivelCuenta}) or(a.EsdeMovimiento=1))] GROUP BY a.Codigo_Cuenta,a.Desc_Cuenta) c WHERE (c.TotDeb<>0) or (c.TotCred<>0) or (c.SaldoAnt<>0) [ or (1 IN ({mostraceros,VALUE})) ]
